      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "4a758230e58d7c74",
      "text": "**Note**: The following passage is similar to TEUBNER, Gunther, 2009. Self-subversive Justice: Contingency or Transcendence Formula of Law? The Modern Law Review. Online. 2009. Vol. 72, no. 1, p. 1–23. [Accessed 31 May 2022].  [https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/full/10.1111/j.1468-2230.2009.00731.x DOI]. \n"
